---
import Layout from '../components/layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Owly Labs">
  <section class="relative z-10 pt-32 pb-24">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-3xl">
      
      <div class="glass-panel p-8 md:p-12">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-foreground mb-2">
          Privacy Policy
        </h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-8">
          Last Updated: December 14, 2025
        </p>
        
        <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-6 text-muted-foreground">
          
          <p class="text-foreground text-lg">
            At Owly Labs, we believe that your voice is part of your identity and your heritage. We are committed to protecting it.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-foreground mt-8 mb-3">1. Information We Collect</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
            <li><strong class="text-foreground">Voice Data:</strong> Audio recordings you voluntarily provide via the Voice Passport.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-foreground">Metadata:</strong> Demographics (e.g., age, dialect region) to help us map linguistic diversity.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-foreground">Usage Data:</strong> How you interact with Aether Voice OS.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-foreground mt-8 mb-3">2. How We Use Your Data</h3>
          <p>
            We use your data for one primary purpose: <strong class="text-foreground">To build AI that understands you.</strong>
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
            <li>Training our speech recognition models to understand non-standard dialects.</li>
            <li>Improving the accuracy of our synthesis engines (with your permission).</li>
            <li>Academic research on linguistic preservation (aggregated and anonymized only).</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-foreground mt-8 mb-3">3. Data Stewardship</h3>
          <p>
            We employ a "Heritage First" approach to data security:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
            <li><strong class="text-foreground">Encryption:</strong> All voice data is encrypted at rest and in transit.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-foreground">No Ad Targeting:</strong> We do not use your voice content to build advertising profiles.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-foreground">Right to Forget:</strong> You can request deletion of your raw voice recordings at any time.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-foreground mt-8 mb-3">4. Contact Us</h3>
          <p>
            If you have questions about your data, please contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@owlylabs.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">privacy@owlylabs.com</a>.
          </p>
          
        </div>
      </div>
      
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
